{"tid":467991,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"香港科技公司成功破解TouchID 解鎖 iPhone 只需一塊牙膠","createTime":"2017-11-14T04:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T01:40:23.000Z","uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ff8534d8808b165e0ce8d26ae2a0bea9dca254","tid":467991,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"iPhone 6S 的 Touch ID 精確度高，採用先進的電容式觸控技術，可從表皮層之下真皮層，擷取指紋小塊局部的高解析度影像，然後 Touch ID 會對這些資訊進行極度仔細且精密的智慧型分析。除了複製指紋之外，破解 Face ID 的難度極高。，然而，有本地保安公司卻成功破解 Touch ID 並解鎖 iPhone 6S，而只需一塊牙膠。<br />\n<br />\n一家香港的科技公司 unwire 發佈了一段香港文的短文，示範如何破解 iPhone 6S Touch ID，在示範之中，他們登錄了測試者的 Touch ID，然後為測試者製作了一個指紋倒模，然而打開 iPhone 6S 螢幕之後，Touch ID 卻以為這個倒模是測試者的指紋解鎖了。<br />\n<br />\n在短文最後部分展示的倒模，你可以看到 Touch ID 會分辨多種指紋特徵，包括弧形紋、箕形紋或斗形紋，其他輪廊卻以白色來表示，換言之集齊了以上的特徵並在比對下發現 Touch ID 的指紋數據一致，就能破解 Touch ID 解鎖 iPhone 6S 了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/image020-1-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2Fimage020-1-694x390.jpg&h=e29e4134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/05/25/fake-fingerprint-to-unlock/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F05%2F25%2Ffake-fingerprint-to-unlock%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2f5de31b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/05/25/fake-fingerprint-to-unlock/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"aada4b942bcb34ef24fac6f86435ef79a88b0305","tid":467991,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bd995895a4d85830312336fe32b22e3204ee39","tid":467991,"uid":57962,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1283dd872ced4ef12a3467b7ce5ac252b49ed4c4","tid":467991,"uid":14918,"like":1,"di